:: Y
As she descends into the dimly lit caverns beneath Irinu, Lyara discovers a grand underground chamber adorned with ancient symbols and relics.
[[Enter to investigate secrets->Z]]
[[Head back to the entrance->AA]]

:: Z
Exploring deeper, Lyara encounters an ornate pedestal holding a dust-covered tome titled 'Chronicles of Eldoria'. As she opens it, ghostly whispers fill her mind with tales of past heroes and forgotten spells.
[[Continue->AB]]

:: AA
Retreating slightly in confusion but guided by curiosity, Lyara finds a hidden lever camouflaged as part of the chamber wall. Pulling it reveals an intricate map depicting Eldoria's secret history.
[[Continue->AB]]

:: AB
'Every path led to shared discoveries.' A local historian enters just then and shares stories that tie both B and C narratives into a deeper understanding, concluding with tales of the current village legends.
[[Continue->X]]
